---
layout: base
title: "Kitchen Fixture Reviews"
description: "Engineering-grade reviews of kitchen faucets, sinks, and fixtures. Spec-first analysis, honest limitations, and total cost of ownership over realistic service life."
permalink: /reviews/kitchen/
---

<div class="container" style="padding-top: 2rem;">

  <h1>Kitchen Fixture Reviews</h1>
  <p class="category-intro">Kitchen infrastructure evaluated on material quality, duty ratings, and 20-year service life expectations — not finish trends.</p>

  <div class="review-list">
    {% for review in collections.kitchenReviews | reverse %}
    <article class="review-card">
      <h2><a href="{{ review.url }}">{{ review.data.title }}</a></h2>
      {% if review.data.description %}<p>{{ review.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
      {% if review.data.date %}<time>{{ review.data.date | dateFormat }}</time>{% endif %}
      <a href="{{ review.url }}" class="read-more">Read full review →</a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

</div>
